701515f-a.title: Bronx: Muliner Avenue - Morris Park Avenue
701515f-a.text:
Muliner Avenue (telephone poles thereon), between
Morris Park and Rhinelander Avenues, showing two frame
houses where Delanoey Place comes up to meet them from
the south. This view is northeastward from Matthews
Avenue. Note Public School No. 83, among the trees.
June 22, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
